<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF806A3FFD229A481DF5B700" authorityName="H. Allen" authorityYear="1862" box="[734,1013,3089,3122]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="123" pageNumber="881" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="intermedius">Lasiurus intermedius</taxonomicName>
1s in the Yellow Bat group. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
